SYMATTR Prefix E
SYMATTR Description Ideal op-amp (single high-gain VCVS, no supply pins), pins: in+ non-inverting(upper-left, "+" mark) in- inverting(lower-left, "-" mark) out(right tip) (chapter figure symbol, custom-drawn triangle, not a copy of the real LTspice UniversalOpamp2 artwork). Value field holds the open-loop gain (e.g. 1e5); emitted as an E-element, see tools/asc_to_net.py.
PIN 0 16 NONE 0
PINATTR PinName IN+
PIN 0 80 NONE 0
PINATTR PinName IN-
PIN 64 48 NONE 0
PINATTR PinName OUT
